				Why would you want items able to be banked? Then you still have naked mages running around taking peoples gear and banking it till they can sell it.... Why not have them have to keep it on them, and then you can get them back and take it back from them. <br>  <br> As for the guys saying a lvl 30 would pikc off a level 1, No, because +5 -5 lvl PVP limit means you can only attack people 5 lvls higher and 5 lvls lower. It would be a true balanced pvp server if all the changes i listed above were to be put in. Trust me, Banks are for coin, not for possessions. Then everyone would HAVE to run around with all their gear on, and would have no where to hide it for only times that they were &quot;safe&quot;. It would be a great server, believe me, ive played games with rules like this and they have worked perfectly. <br>  <br> -Nifield of KoT. &quot;We deliver&quot;		

